Enum Clearinghouse

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Clearinghouse>
no.uio.ifi.clearinghouse.Clearinghouse
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Clearinghouse>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Clearinghouse
extends java.lang.Enum<Clearinghouse>
Singleton class to to be used for getting visa JWT tokens provided access JWT token and for converting visa JWT tokens to Visa POJOs.

    • getVisaTokens
